    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:47px;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1" style="text-align:left; text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="New_Add_icon4.bmp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Heading1" style="color:#000000;"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="New_Add_icon4.bmp" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Heading1" style="font-size:12pt; color:#000000;"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Can I copy a pacing guide and use it for the next school year? ]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading1" style="text-align:left; text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; color:#000080;" translate="true">Yes, a pacing guide can be copied and used for the next year. &#160;In order to do this you will need to use the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;" translate="true">Copy Content From</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; color:#000080;" translate="true"> option on the new pacing guide. Go to the pacing guide for the new school year and there will be an option in the left nav, under the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;" translate="true">Actions </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; color:#000080;" translate="true">section, called </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;" translate="true">Copy Content From. &#160;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; color:#000080;" translate="true">This option will open a new window that will allow you to search for old pacing guides to copy to the new one, you just need to select the correct plan and click the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;" translate="true">Add Curriculum Plan</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; color:#000080;" translate="true"> button.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
